6 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT PROVIDING AN INCOME TAX CREDIT FOR VOLUNTEER
7 EMERGENCY FIRST RESPONDERS; PROVIDING ELIGIBILITY REQUIREMENTS; PROVIDING THAT THE
8 CREDIT IS REFUNDABLE; AMENDING SECTION 15-30-2303, MCA; AND PROVIDING AN APPLICABILITY
9 DATE.”
